Important: indentation is required! Code inside if must be indented (usually 4 spaces).

if condition:
    # code if true
else:
    # code if false

if condition1:
    # code if condition1 is true
elif condition2:
    # code if condition2 is true
else:
    # code if all conditions are false

You can use as many elif as needed.

en.codeExample:
